#Cavity Geometry
brick x {x_cav} y {y_cav} z {z_cav}
move volume 1 z {z_cav/2} include_merged

#Injection Pipe 
create cylinder height {y_cav+4.05*2} radius {rad_pipe}
rotate volume 2 angle 90 about x include_merged
move Volume 2 z {inj_loc} include_merged

#outlet Pipe 
create cylinder height {y_cav+4.05*2} radius {sol_rad_pipe}
rotate volume 3 angle 90 about x include_merged
move Volume 3 z {sol_loc} include_merged

chop volume 2 with volume 1  keep 
chop volume 3 with volume 1  keep 
delete volume 2 3
split body 5 7
delete volume 6, 8
chop volume 1  with volume 4 
chop volume 11  with volume 7 

create Cylinder height 64 radius 4
rotate Volume 14  angle 90  about X include_merged  
move Volume 14  z {inj_loc} include_merged  
intersect volume 13 14  keep 
delete volume 14
remove overlap volume 13 15 modify volume 13

brick x 15 y {y_cav} z 15
move volume 17 z {inj_loc} include_merged
webcut volume 13  with plane from surface 58  
webcut volume 13  with plane from surface 60  
webcut volume 18 13 19  with plane from surface 55  
webcut volume 20 21 22  with plane from surface 56  
delete volume 17

brick x 2 y {y_cav} z 2
move volume 26 z {sol_loc} include_merged
webcut volume 24 23 25  with plane from surface 141  
webcut volume 28 27 29  with plane from surface 142  
webcut volume 27  with plane from surface 146  
webcut volume 27  with plane from surface 144  
delete volume 26

webcut volume 23 24 25  with plane zplane offset 12
webcut volume all with plane yplane offset 6 

